The plugin interfaces to a network monitor application. It allows the user to setup network monitoring. Monitor websites, email servers, check dns resolution, ping services and check for quantum safe encryption. Monitor data is stored and can be retrieved and analysed to give useful information about the status of a service over time. The user will receive email alerts when their host is down.

For testing purposes you can use to login:
username:  signup2@mahadeva.co.uk 
password openaitest

Alternatively you can register your own user by clicking 'Create an account'

Prompts :

Show me the current hosts being monitored.

Give me the latest monitoring data for https://freenetworkmonitor.click

Add a new host to monitor https://www.bbc.co.uk



